name: Trantorian
intro: Space-themed MMO, grand strategy video game
introduce: Trantorian is a NFT-based 3D space exploration, battle, economic and civilization development game situated on a persistent, ever-growing metaverse. By leveraging Sui’s decentralized, gamer-friendly blockchain, Trantorian bridges the best of traditional games with the added benefits of on-chain technology, innovation, and data structures.
